name: Wing It (itch) (BharathK33, Precizne, Nivo, grx6741)
description:
Description: 

Bounce along as you try to escape the dangerous rocks falling with our young bird Bord (not a typo, please don't be bored).

 How to Play:

 -> Use your mouse to propel Bord.

 -> When you click the mouse, the bird flaps away from it. (ig birds hate mouses)

 -> Press escape to exit the game
